            <title>Mickey Mouse 版權元旦到期，美國導演即上傳 Mickey 恐怖片預告</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/03/mickey-mouse-horror/movie-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mickey-mouse-horror</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/03/mickey-mouse-horror/movie-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 12:30:42 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影視娛樂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Disney]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mickey Mouse]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[版權法]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1212880</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div class="x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a"><div dir="auto">Disney 旗下著名動畫角色米奇（Mickey Mouse）於《Steamboat Willie》亮相的版本根據美國版權法規定，在今年元旦正式進入公有領域，來自美國的導演 Jamie Bailey 隨即與其團隊在 YouTube 上傳了第一條以 Mickey Mouse 為主角的恐怖電影《Mickey&#8217;s Mouse Trap》的預告片。</div><div dir="auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1212974" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-01-03-72426-513x580.jpg" alt="" width="513" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-01-03-72426-513x580.jpg 513w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-01-03-72426-796x900.jpg 796w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-01-03-72426-768x868.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/2024-01-03-72426.jpg 1338w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 513px" /></div><div dir="auto"></div></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><p>《Mickey&#8217;s Mouse Trap》故事背景設定於女主角 21 歲生日當日，由於她要在遊樂場上班，因此無法與朋友慶祝生辰。女主角的朋友決定給她一個驚喜，在遊樂場為女主角慶祝生日，可是一個頭戴 Mickey Mouse 面具的殺手混入了樂園，因此主角需要用盡一切方法，逃離殺手的追捕。</p></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1212934" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/412840269_737827935071907_5231297061018041740_n-1-694x448.png" alt="" width="694" height="448" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/412840269_737827935071907_5231297061018041740_n-1-694x448.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/412840269_737827935071907_5231297061018041740_n-1-1280x826.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/412840269_737827935071907_5231297061018041740_n-1-768x495.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/412840269_737827935071907_5231297061018041740_n-1-1536x991.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/412840269_737827935071907_5231297061018041740_n-1-2048x1321.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/412840269_737827935071907_5231297061018041740_n-1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto">電影中除了殺手頭戴 Mickey Mouse 面具外，預告片中亦有不少《Steamboat Willie》的元素，配合預告片上傳的時間，可見拍攝影團隊早就對 Mickey Mosue 版權進入公共領域一事做好準備。</div><div dir="auto"></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1212884" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-0-31-screenshot-694x295.png" alt="" width="694" height="295" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-0-31-screenshot-694x295.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-0-31-screenshot-1280x545.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-0-31-screenshot-768x327.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-0-31-screenshot-1536x654.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-0-31-screenshot-2048x871.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-0-31-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲預告片中可見《Steamboat Willie》的海報，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kAg7laUDXX4">YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1212885" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-1-0-screenshot-694x295.png" alt="" width="694" height="295" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-1-0-screenshot-694x295.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-1-0-screenshot-1280x545.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-1-0-screenshot-768x327.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-1-0-screenshot-1536x654.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-1-0-screenshot-2048x871.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MICKEYS-MOUSE-TRAP-FILM-TEASER-TRAILER-2024-FIRST-EVER-MICKEY-MOUSE-HORROR-FILM-1-0-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kAg7laUDXX4">YouTube</a></p><p>《Mickey&#8217;s Mouse Trap》編劇兼製片 Simon Philips 接受 BBC 採訪時表示，他們僅是想製作一部有趣的電影，同時又稱，如果繼續將 Mickey Mouse 放在闔家歡電影裏面，那麼永遠不會有突破，因此他們想做一些與 Mickey Mouse 以往形象有很大反差的事。現階段 Simon Philips 尚未透露電影何時上映，但消息指預計將於今年 3 月上映。</p><p>Mickey Mosue 並非第一個被套進恐怖電影的 Disney 角色，2022 年 Disney 旗下角色 Winnie the Pooh 就搶先步進入公共財產領域，其後英國導演 Rhys Frake-Waterfield 自編自導《Winnie-the-Pooh: Blood and Honey》電影。劇情講述 Christopher Robin 上大學後就拋棄了小熊維尼與小豬，於是他們就大開殺戒。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1212891" src="https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MV5BNGMwNjBlM2MtYzFlNi00ZDgwLTkwN2QtMjgzOWVjMWQ4NzAzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDA1NDA2NTk@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_-454x580.jpg" alt="" width="454" height="580" srcset="https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MV5BNGMwNjBlM2MtYzFlNi00ZDgwLTkwN2QtMjgzOWVjMWQ4NzAzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDA1NDA2NTk@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_-454x580.jpg 454w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MV5BNGMwNjBlM2MtYzFlNi00ZDgwLTkwN2QtMjgzOWVjMWQ4NzAzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDA1NDA2NTk@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_-704x900.jpg 704w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MV5BNGMwNjBlM2MtYzFlNi00ZDgwLTkwN2QtMjgzOWVjMWQ4NzAzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDA1NDA2NTk@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_-768x982.jpg 768w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MV5BNGMwNjBlM2MtYzFlNi00ZDgwLTkwN2QtMjgzOWVjMWQ4NzAzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDA1NDA2NTk@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 454px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt19623240/">IMDb</a></p><p>初代 Mickey Mouse 於 1928 年，在黑白動畫短片《Steamboat Willie》中首次登場，至今已歷經 95 個寒暑，其與初代 Minnie Mouse 版權亦正式在今年元旦日到期，意味着創作者不需再經由 Disney 許可或付費就能夠使用這個版本的 Mickey Mouse。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_96091"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kAg7laUDXX4?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-67861538">BBC</a>、<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" dir="auto" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kAg7laUDXX4&amp;ab_channel=SimonPhillipsActor">Simon Phillips Actor@ YouTube</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/03/mickey-mouse-horror/movie-2/">Mickey Mouse 版權元旦到期，美國導演即上傳 Mickey 恐怖片預告</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
